# reorG Grid / Table Conventions

## Row Model

- One main row = one master-store SKU group (MasterRow + linked MarketplaceListings)
- NOT one row per marketplace listing, NOT one row per store
- Shared internal values (weight, supplier cost, supplier shipping) display once at row level
- Store-specific values (sale price, profit, ad rate, item IDs) display as uniform mini-blocks inside the cell

## Store Mini-Blocks

- Each store-specific cell contains equal-size mini-blocks tagged with store acronym (TPP, TT, BC, SHPFY)
- Mini-blocks must be visually uniform and aligned across rows
- Use store logos/icons where helpful
- Support multiple blocks per store (duplicate listings for same SKU)
- Empty store slots should not cause layout shifts — use consistent sizing

## Frozen Columns

- Default frozen: UPC, Item IDs, SKU, Title
- User can unfreeze via Settings
- Frozen columns stay visible during horizontal scroll

## Search

- Sticky at top of the grid page; hideable via user preference
- Dynamic autocomplete — no need to press Enter
- Search by: UPC, Item ID, SKU, Title
- Support prefix, contains, and fuzzy typo tolerance
- Selecting a result scrolls/jumps to the row in the virtualized grid

## Variations

- Parent row = synthetic grouping row
- Child rows = indented underneath, clearly labeled
- Collapsed by default; expandable
- Auto-collapse on page refresh

## Sorting and Density

- Default sort: alphabetical by master-store title
- Comfortable density default; density toggle available

## Cell Editing

- Editable cells: Sale Price, Promoted Ad Rate (push-enabled); Weight, Supplier Cost, Supplier Shipping, Platform Fee (internal only)
- Edits autosave to StagedChange after 500ms debounce
- Edits recalculate dependent values (profit, shipping cost) immediately on client
- Edits never auto-push to marketplaces

## Staged Visual Treatment

- Staged values: prominent display with purple staged badge
- Live values: smaller, shown underneath for comparison
- Use subtle highlight — not error-red
- Compare drawer available for detailed inspection
